# calc_delimiters_smoke.numos — Phase 10B. Render sin(30) in the real
# CalculationApp to confirm normal-height delimiters (which use the bundled
# stix_math parenthesis glyph directly, NOT the vector fallback) still look
# clean alongside the polished tall-delimiter path. Warning-only (no golden).
log "calc delimiters: start"
wait 200
open_app Calc
wait 60
key sin
key 3
key 0
key enter
wait 100
screenshot out/calc_sin30.ppm
assert_app Calculation
log "calc delimiters: sin(30) rendered"
